Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  瓜生…
